= Emergency Ordinance for the Reactivation of Economy

Papen has taken the initiative on economic matters, using the funds generated by the gutting of the unemployment insurance program to finance tax cuts for the wealthy and their businesses. This has solidified the backing of the industrial elite behind his chancellorship, but further cements his image as a chancellor for the barons.

However, it does help draw bourgeois sympathies into the cabinet, as many upper-class members of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center</span> and various bourgeois parties applaud his effort toward constructive policy.

